+# Bolt Integration - Estable
+
+This folder contains helper scripts and ABI export for Bolt.new integration and for deploying to Base Sepolia.
+
+How to use:
+
+1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and set `PRIVATE_KEY`, `BASE_RPC`, `TREASURY_ADDRESS`, etc.
+2. Install dependencies at repo root:
+   ```bash
+   npm install
+   ```
+3. Compile contracts:
+   ```bash
+   npx hardhat compile
+   ```
+4. Export ABIs for frontend:
+   ```bash
+   node bolt_integration/scripts/export_abis.js
+   ```
+5. Deploy everything (timelock + factory, and optional example vault):
+   ```bash
+   node bolt_integration/scripts/deploy_all.js
+   ```
+
+Bolt usage:
+- Push repo to GitHub and connect Bolt.new to it.
+- Bolt will detect scripts under `bolt_integration/scripts` and show deploy buttons.
